oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Performance - Claire Lynch Band - 2013-11-09
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by Claire Lynch and her band as part of the Bluegrass and Beyond program from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on November 9, 2013. Fourth performance of four. Presented by the Crump familly and Cotten Music Center. Honoring George A. and Marjorie S. Crump.
